balinese: Basa warisan sane sampun…berabad-abad ring jagate. Angge pisan (basa Bali)!
english: Heritage language that centuries in the world. Use it (the Balinese language)!
indonesian: Bahasa warisan yang sudah berabad-abad di dunia. Pakailah (bahasa Bali)!

balinese: Eda bes sanget kenehanga, nyanan lempuyengan. Nika sampun, Kak, punapi carane ngilangang?
english: Don’t think too much about it, you may get headache later. That’s true, Grandpa, how to relieve it?
indonesian: Jangan terlalu dipikirkan, nanti pusing. Itu dia, Kek, bagaimana cara menghilangkannya?
